c: 43
v: 38
t: "Kugeza ubwo (uwirengagije urwibutso) azatugeraho (akerekwa iherezo rye ribi), maze avuge (abwira shitani yamuyobeje) ati “Iyo hagati yanjye nawe haza kuba hari intera ingana nk’iri hagati y’uburasirazuba n’uburengerazuba (simbe narakugize inshuti). Mbega ukuntu wambereye inshuti mbi!”"